#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31467"
msgid "Welcome to Madnox! For the best experience, we recommend applying the default settings. This will configure all visual options and features. Would you like to apply the Madnox recommended settings now?"
msgstr "Welkom by Madnox! Vir die beste ervaring, beveel ons aan dat u die verstekinstellings toepas. Dit sal alle visuele opsies en kenmerke opstel. Wil u die aanbevole Madnox-instellings nou toepas?"

#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31468"
msgid "This will restore all skin settings to their original defaults.[CR][CR]Your current customizations will be lost.[CR]Are you sure you want to continue?"
msgstr "Dit sal alle vel-instellings na hul oorspronklike verstekwaardes herstel.[CR][CR]U huidige aanpassings sal verlore gaan.[CR]Is u seker u wil voortgaan?"

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31470"
msgid "Restore Madnox skin settings to day 1 out of the box startup values. Only affects skin settings, does not alter or change anything else like scripts or plugins."
msgstr "Herstel Madnox-velinstellings na dag 1 uit-die-boks-beginwaardes. Beïnvloed slegs vel-instellings, verander niks anders soos skripte of inproppe nie."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31471"
msgid "Allows customization of default media flags without requiring outside hacks to the skin. This allows you to custom select which video container icons will be displayed for WebDL, 1080p, 720p etc. This can be reset at any time."
msgstr "Laat pasmaking van verstek-mediavlae toe sonder om eksterne bakkerye aan die vel te vereis. Dit laat jou toe om self te kies watter video-houer-ikone vertoon sal word vir WebDL, 1080p, 720p ens. Dit kan enige tyd teruggestel word."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31472"
msgid "Enables setting of the color of \"In-Progress\" bar feature."
msgstr "Aktiveer die opstel van die kleur vir die \"Besig-om-te-kyk\"-vorderingsbalk."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Sets of the color of \"In-Progress\" bar feature globally when enabled."
msgstr "Stel die kleur van die \"Besig-om-te-kyk\"-vorderingsbalk globaal in wanneer dit geaktiveer is."

