msgstr "Huidige ingeboude hersieningsvlak van die verstek Madnox-waardes om die vel terug te stel / te inisieer."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31507"
msgid "Select if an intro video will play when Kodi is first started. None: No video, Built-In: Kodi's release level intro video, Custom: Pick video of your choice to display."
msgstr "Kies of 'n inleidingsvideo sal speel wanneer Kodi die eerste keer begin word. Geen: Geen video, Ingebou: Kodi se vrystellingsvlak-inleidingsvideo, Pasgemaak: Kies 'n video van jou keuse om te vertoon."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Hierdie instelling dwing die mediavlag na die resolusievlag as 4K of 2160p, wat gebruikers-ikoongrondbeheer bied sonder vel-wysigings."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31509"
msgid "Change the stars color displayed in the video info line. Click to cycle through fixed colors or select a custom color."
msgstr "Verander die kleur van die sterre wat in die video-inligtingslyn vertoon word. Klik om deur vaste kleure te blaai of kies 'n pasgemaakte kleur."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31510"
msgid "Allows star ratings style to use a custom color when it is set to \"Custom\"."
msgstr "Laat toe dat stergradering-styl 'n pasgemaakte kleur gebruik wanneer dit op \"Pasgemaak\" gestel is."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "Toegewyde byvoeging vir Madnox vereis vir Piers+. Skuif alle vrylopende skripte na 'n toegewyde byvoeging om sekuriteitsredes."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "TMDbHelper bied verskeie gereedskap om vel-ontwerpers te help om inligting van TMDb-, OMDb- en Trakt-API's te verkry."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
msgstr "Wikipedia-byvoeging vir Kodi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "Gevorderde CinemaVision-vervanging wat geaktiveer kan word om Madnox se ingeboude eenvoudiger CinemaMode te vervang. Bied die uiteindelike CinemaMode-ervaring en pasmaking."

#: /16x9/Includes_CustomSelect.xml
msgctxt "#31515"
msgid "Blur with color"
msgstr "Vag met kleur"

