msgctxt "#31520"
msgid "This will re-run the optional extras installer. All extras will be downloaded and installed in a disabled state. Enable only what you need in Settings > Skin Settings > Addons."
msgstr "Dit sal die opsionele ekstras-installeerder herloop. Alle ekstras sal afgelaai en in 'n gedeaktiveerde toestand geïnstalleer word. Aktiveer slegs wat u benodig in Instellings > Vel-instellings > Byvoegings."

