msgstr "Laat veranderinge aan die graderings toe om tussen desimale getalle of as 'n persentasie om te skakel. Beïnvloed TMDb & IMDb, alle ander behou hul verstekvertoning."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31525"
msgid "Re-run skin shortcuts migrator"
msgstr "Herloop velkortpaaie-migreerder"

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31526"
msgid "This will rewrite the skin shortcuts .properties file to the current 3 module addon structure. Only run if there are issues with background images or playlists are not working."
msgstr "Dit sal die velkortpaaie .properties-lêer na die huidige 3-module-byvoegingstruktuur herskryf. Loop slegs as daar probleme met agtergrondbeelde is of as snitlyste nie werk nie."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31527"
msgid "This will reactivate the addons installer. Only run if addons were not installed when skin was first installed."
msgstr "Dit sal die byvoegingsinstalleerder heraktiveer. Loop slegs as byvoegings nie geïnstalleer was toe die vel die eerste keer geïnstalleer is nie."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31528"
